name: Henery Stickman: 2D Platformer Games
description:
Henery stickman is on a mission to survive his 2D platformer world that has suddenly turned cruel. A 2D platform games with abstract graphics will bring you immense difficulty and challenges from the obstacles.

Help Henery Stickman stand against these obstacles and enjoy facing the challenges increasing at every level in this 2D Platform Games. This Hard Game will provide you tough competition, your agility and patience will make you win this game easily.
